Nobel Design Holdings Limited




 

 
















 





Nobel Design Holdings Ltd is a public listed company in Singapore engaged in interior design for residential, offi ce and commercial purposes. The company offers a comprehensive range of products and services from turnkey interior design, renovation, home styling, retail of furniture and home accessories to furniture manufacturing. Nobel Design has offi ces in Brunei, China, Indonesia, Malaysia and Singapore. 


