nobel design holdings ltd (547) Details


			Nobel Design Holdings Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the furniture retail, interior design, supply chain management, hotel, and property development businesses. It is involved in the retail of designer furniture, office furniture, leather chairs, and other office accessories; trading and distribution on an e-commerce platform for furniture, accessories, fabrics, and furnishings for the business-to-business markets; sourcing, supply chain management, wholesale, and Internet retail of furniture, accessories, fabrics, and furnishings; and provision of turnkey project and project management services. The company also provides interior design and renovation services for homes, offices, and commercial projects; manufactures and supplies furniture, furnishing, lighting, and building material products; supplies and installs furniture and fittings; retails upmarket European furniture and accessories to end-users and specifier market; offers home styling services; and retails soft furnishing products. In addition, it supplies furniture to hotels, service apartments, clubs, restaurants, showflats, offices, and homes; decoration accessories; and interior design contract services. The company has operations in Singapore, Malaysia, Brunei, the United States, and the United Kingdom. Nobel Design Holdings Ltd was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Singapore.
  			

