Company Description                    




                        Nobel Design Holdings Ltd is a holding company engaged in  interior designing and renovation services for homes, supply & installation of custom-made furniture and fittings, turnkey project and project management. The company also engaged in distributes and retail  fine imported European home furnishings brands and has conceptualized and retail its house-labels such as "Marquis", "Lifestory", "Minotti by Marquis Interiors", "Marquis Studio" and "extremely fashionable furniture OM". In addition, Nobel Design Holdings expanded into property development under ACT-Nobel Homes Pte Ltd, a joint venture with ACT Holdings Pte Ltd. The company developed numerous boutiques, residential projects and luxury homes. The company's headquarters is in Singapore with offices in the United States of America and around Asia. Nobel Design Holdings Ltd was incorporated in 1981.                    


